            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has slightly softened, add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> to the pan with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp]<strong> </span>flour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
